<body>

  <% include ../views/partials/_header %>
  <div class ="transparent-box">

    <section class="flexcontainer">
      <div class="menus">
        <img alt="picture" src="/images/trueblood.jpg">
        <h2>True Blood Vials</h2>
        <p>
          Our blood is drawn fresh from our in-house, organic humans, or for our vegetarian
          clientele, our tasty synthetic house recipe (we swear, you won't be able to tell the difference)!
        </p>
        <button class = "atc" id ="6" type="submit">Add to Cart</button>
      </div>

      <div class="menus">
        <img alt="picture" src="/images/bloodpunch.jpg">
        <h2>Blood Punch</h2>
        <p>
          Our organic, locally sourced blood spiked with booze for when you need that little extra kick!
          Perfect for when you're hosting a soiree with your undead friends.
        </p>
        <button class = "atc" id ="2" type="submit">Add to Cart</button>
      </div>

      <div class="menus">
        <img alt="picture" src="/images/fangcookies.jpg">
        <h2>Fang Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Enjoy your Fang Cookies with chocolate chips and a chewy marshmallow and blood-filled centre.
          Perfect for kindred children and those creatures of the night with a bit of a sweet tooth.
        </p>
        <button class = "atc" id ="10" type="submit">Add to Cart</button>
      </div>

    </section>

    <section class="flexcontainer">
      
      <div class="menus">
        <img alt="picture" src="/images/bloodcupcakes.jpg">
        <h2>Bloody Cupcakes</h2>
        <p>Bite down on our fluffy vanilla cupcakes and you'll discover a gooey, blood-filled centre.
          Perfect for those fussy kindred children with a sweet tooth or for the more innocent among our kind. 
        </p>
        <button class = "atc" id ="3" type="submit">Add to Cart</button>
      </div>


      <div class="menus">
        <img alt="picture" src="/images/cocktail.jpg">
        <h2>Drippy Blood Cocktail</h2>
        <p>
          An exotic fusion of distilled schnapps, congealed fat and the blood of a virgin make our Drippy
          Blood Cocktail a treat for the night creatures with refined sensibilities.
        </p>
       <button class = "atc" id ="4" type="submit">Add to Cart</button>
      </div>


      <div class="menus">
        <img alt="picture" src="/images/biteshots.jpg">
        <h2>Bite Shots</h2>
        <p>
          Bite sized shots of our in-house true blood (comes in vegetarian or organic human options) 
          mixed with whisky for a bit of a kick. Perfect for the modern vampire on-the-go.
        </p>
        <button class = "atc" id ="5" type="submit">Add to Cart</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="flexcontainer">
      <div class="menus">
        <img alt="picture" src="/images/slayersoup.jpg">
        <h2>Slayer Soup</h2>
        <p>Live on the edge with our garlic-infused Slayer Soup.
          Sometimes being immortal can be a bit of a bore, so why not live on the edge like a mortal?
          Order this soup and you may not live through the night.
        </p>
        <button class = "atc" id ="1" type="submit">Add to Cart</button>
        </div>


      <div class="menus">
        <img alt="picture" src="/images/heart.png">
        <h2>Fresh Bloody Hearts</h2>
        <p>
          These hearts have been skillfully filleted from their human hosts and are served whole on a bed of 
          dandelion greens with parsnip and blood infused puree. A decadent and hearty meal.
        </p>
        <button class = "atc" id ="7" type="submit">Add to Cart</button>
      </div>

      <div class="menus">
        <img alt="picture" src="/images/fleshbuds.png">
        <h2>Flesh Rosebuds</h2>
        <p>
          Tiny chunks of juicy human fat cubed into neat squares and decorated with rosebuds
          folded from human flesh. Drizzled in a light blood syrup. Perfect for a refined vampiric dinner-party. 
        </p>
        <button class = "atc" id ="8" type="submit">Add to Cart</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="flexcontainer">
      <div class="menus">
        <img alt="picture" src="/images/cheekshanks.jpg">
        <h2>Cheek Shanks with Blood Reduction</h2>
        <p>Our finely carved sheek shanks are served in a syrupy blood reduction that has 
          simmered for hours to obtain its deep, woody flavour and thick consistency. 
        </p>
        <button class = "atc" id ="9" type="submit">Add to Cart</button>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>

